其他员工造成了不良的负面影响，二审法院认定张某娟在工位上打伞的行为属于严重违反了公司劳动纪律的情形并无不妥，公司据此解除与张某娟之间的劳动合同，合法合理。 最终，广东省高级人民法院裁定，驳回张某娟的再审申请。公司安装监控女子担心走光打伞上班被开除，索赔 33 万被驳回 _ 赔偿"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-0f9bc31ef125d85bea6600ab7cfb74a8_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "38 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/466782388"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IuYS8x4rVtb0LEAMaCDY2MDA4NzYwIKKxy4YGMEA4owlAKXIJNDY2NzgyMzg4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1624585870.553851", "card_id": "Q_376567574", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 166}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "CPU 的性能是不是快到天花板了？为什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-93af83a565db2d43e9816ecf8365d404_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "35 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/376567574"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IuYS8x4rVtb0LEAMaCDQ1OTU5NzI4INqi+vIFMA844Q1AKnIJMzc2NTY3NTc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1624585870.5543013", "card_id": "Q_466663677", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 134}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "我还是没有完全理解幸存者偏差，有人能解释一下吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "有简单易理解的回答吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "32 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/466663677"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IuYS8x4rVtb0LEAMaCDY1OTgyMzkwIPmhyIYGMAU45AFAK3IJNDY2NjYzNjc3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1624585870.5545702", "card_id": "Q_455984065", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 154}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你用过最好用的小家电是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {